Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从国王开始走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被利瓦尔带走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是代打?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是扑克还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩完全没有身为学生会会员的自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在赌钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑明明那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路却总是用在奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好学习的话 成绩什么的...对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想说『我们家的小鲁路明明是个认真的好孩子』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易偷出来却...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪玉城那家伙不按直人的作战计划去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵族太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要保住面子  所以一定会付钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上你还创造了8分32秒的新记录
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的持子时间又不长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在的贵族们都长在温室里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是寄生在特权之下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要和11区的人玩玩看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们布里塔尼亚人不一样...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了  把无关的人都卷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区的人真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是布里塔尼亚第三皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯殿下演讲的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[克洛维斯·La·布里塔尼亚  Clovis La Britannia]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位帝国的臣民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  还有大多数配合我们的11区住民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是什么11区住民  是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我的内心被撕成了两半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被分成了悲伤与愤怒之心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被赋予了11区的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会向恐怖事件屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说为什么  因为这是正义之战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护所有人幸福的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起向为正义而捐躯的8名烈士致以哀悼之意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,默哀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你不做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,况且即使我们哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的人也不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好伤感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底也只是自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算站得再直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正世界也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想象不出您之前正在享受宴会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督这个职位是11区的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要学会收放自如
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您真有自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是作为总督必需的思想准备  而不是什么自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做这些不过是为了让媒体的众人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只期望能为克洛维斯殿下的治国尽一份心力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度的治国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  军人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是特别派遣那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[特别派遣向导技术部，通称特别派遣]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少有点能用来做素材的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[因为C.C.的研究是秘密进行，所以可能对外宣称是医疗研究]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察说不过是医疗设备盗走事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不至于动用全军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发动直属军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightMare也出动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一级警报  一级警报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第四  第七  对陆战攻击部队立刻到第三出发口待机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第九特殊师团出击准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一开始就下国王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,国王不动  部下怎么会跟来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修莫非想当社长高官之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的梦想都会破灭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么悠闲地驾驶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  那边是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  难道是我们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报告本厅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标冲进了开发途中被废弃的通用大厦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事已由军队接手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴托雷将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要回收那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  鲁路修  电源线好像断了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  事故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是些笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  谁去帮他们一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  学生救护队登场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说谁去叫一下警察啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的事虽然是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不要做比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不扔下无意义的善心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上课会迟到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永田  永田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  停车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,方向完全倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,货车里至少也装个梯子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻停车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在服从命令的话  还能留你们一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍  现在立刻停车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连军队都出动了  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是为此而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在出去很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像情况很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用手机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从小路进入地下铁路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  我们用那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[卡莲·修坦菲尔德 Kallen Stadtfeld]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不成虐杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里啊  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不去学校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标离开市区向贫民区开去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[Getto：11区人（日本人）居住地，是贫民聚集区]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  继续追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[Slash Haken：即从Glasgow和Sutherland等\N机体装甲胸部两侧发射的锚射缆绳]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Slash Haken
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真正的恐怖分子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的威力你们应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你从哪里搞到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但旧式的Glasgow是赢不了这Sutherland的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况你还是无法理解皇帝陛下仁爱的11区的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  想别的办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是单纯的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,废铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  应变能力不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机没信号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从昏暗程度和路面状况来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以肯定是在过去的地下铁路上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地是平民区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出去会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  明白了 条件都理清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只能借助军队的保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要用恐怖分子的通信器做见面礼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我把他给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我扔下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  难道我猜中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做的太过火了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将军你和克洛维斯殿下悄悄藏起来的某样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被恐怖分子抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想要夺回来是很简单啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还想把他们的同伙一起扫除干净
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要追踪恐怖分子就会知道他们的大本营在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的推理完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个  我只是觉得这件事有点奇怪...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们特派到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了 只是想要帮你大扫除而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我想要资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个被抢走的东西  到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,化学武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  毒气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖组织潜伏在地下铁路的角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的目的就是找到被恐怖分子抢去的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索11区的居民区  新宿贫民区以及地铁路线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现之后立刻报告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标的回收交由我们亲卫队来执行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们虽然是名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过原本还是11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收起你们原本猴子的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获得携带枪支的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,努力取得功绩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是你们向布里塔尼亚显示忠诚的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是事故吗?  还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  扇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,404号发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  立刻准备回收
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在爬到上面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再继续杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且居然用毒气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正这毒气也是布里塔尼亚制造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么不要再继续杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就毁了布里塔尼亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  朱雀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  变成布里塔尼亚的军人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是...毒气?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  慌乱中找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Glasgow的无线电还能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  那个果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就像情报所说的  应该是毒气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为应该是在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回答啊  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩会是毒气?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是指示里的确是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉布里塔尼亚人没有做这种事的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我听说那应该是毒气才对...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有狡辩的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是足以让朱雀的上司们惹上麻烦的猛毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是基于你的功绩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个把恐怖分子给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是普通人  只不过被卷进这件事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是向布里塔尼亚宣誓效忠了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射杀平民  射杀他这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的样子应该是布里塔尼亚的学生吧  真是不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把那女孩抓起来  学生就地射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的混蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本  万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说被他们逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这样还算是亲卫队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然爆风已从上方扩散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是岩盘被...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我到底为什么只把情报告诉你们?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我们继续进行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作战需要进入下一个阶段了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那东西被外界知道了话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会被废黜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向本国说这是军事演习造成的不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以第三皇子克洛维斯的身份命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底毁灭新宿贫民区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么布里塔尼亚会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下来是楼上一层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是连名誉布里塔尼亚人都不如的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不留全部抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚管理官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[杰雷米亚·哥特瓦尔德 Jeremiah·Gottwald,纯血派,边境伯]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴托雷将军想让你接下第二方面军的指挥权
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还有参谋在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的前线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好享受一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是由于你吧 这种混乱...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚把朱雀也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被投入前线了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我们把Lancelot带来了还这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想要出动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有可以驾驶的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里好好待着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有11区住民而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近应该有一个出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,旧市外的地图的确是这么画的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然挂了  勒鲁那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是符合恐怖分子临死前的形象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  作为一个学生你已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的话我也不想杀你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能对上面这么报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了恐怖组织的大本营并将其剿灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人质已经被他们杀光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  这位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀也是  这女孩也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都要结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都还没做到  就轻易的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不想结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像有渴望活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,获得力量的话就能活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是契约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我赐予你力量  作为交换  你只要实现我一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是签订了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能继续生存
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但将作为与人类不同的存在活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,王的力量会使你孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有这个觉悟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诸神黄昏的继续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神话再一次展开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缔结这契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你  仇恨布里塔尼亚人的布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该如何活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是主义者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[主义者:对布里塔尼亚帝国现有政策不满的布里塔尼亚人]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  不开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对手只是个学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有开枪资格的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那些有觉悟被射杀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以鲁路修·Vi·布里塔尼亚之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[Lelouch·Vi·Britannia：鲁路修的真名]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵照您的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一直在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活着是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名字也是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,经历也是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已厌倦了这个毫无改变的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但这谎言让人绝望到想放弃都不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
